1. *Mušterija* je došla u prodavnicu da kupi hleb. (The *customer* came to the store to buy bread.)
2. Konobar je pitao *mušteriju* šta bi želela da naruči. (The waiter asked the *customer* what she would like to order.)
3. *Mušterijama* se svidela nova kolekcija u butiku. (The *customers* liked the new collection at the boutique.)
4. Prodavac je bio ljubazan prema *mušteriji* i pomogao joj da odabere pravi proizvod. (The salesperson was kind to the *customer* and helped her choose the right product.)
5. U restoranu su svi bili zauzeti, ali je *mušterija* bila strpljiva i sačekala svoj red. (The restaurant was busy, but the *customer* was patient and waited her turn.)
6. *Mušterija* je bila nezadovoljna uslugom i tražila je da govori sa menadžerom. (The *customer* was dissatisfied with the service and asked to speak with the manager.)
7. Frizerka je preporučila *mušteriji* da proba novu farbu za kosu. (The hairdresser recommended to the *customer* to try a new hair dye.)
8. Ukoliko *mušterija* ne bude zadovoljna proizvodom, može da ga vrati u roku od 30 dana. (If the *customer* is not satisfied with the product, she can return it within 30 days.)
9. *Mušterije* su često lojalne određenim brendovima i kupuju samo njihove proizvode. (The *customers* are often loyal to certain brands and only buy their products.)
10. Konobarica je bila uslužna i brzo je donela piće *mušteriji*. (The waitress was helpful and quickly brought the drink to the *customer*.)